    <h1>Retargeting Pixel</h1>
    <p class="description">A JavaScript snippet installed on your website that tracks visitor actions and adds them to advertising audience lists — so your ads can follow them across other platforms after they leave without converting.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
      <div class="meta-author">
        <div class="meta-avatar">AVR</div>
